OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 02 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1953FThe Coronation of Queen
OL,7,FElizabeth II is broadcast live on BBC
OL,8,FTV.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThis first televised Coronation took 16
OL,11,Fmonths of planning.
OL,12,
OL,13,FBBC TV went on air earlier than usual
OL,14,Fthat day - at 9.15am - radiating the
OL,15,Ftest card, to allow viewers more time
OL,16,Fto adjust their aerials
OL,17,
OL,18,F20.4 million people watched at least
OL,19,Fhalf an hour of the service - almost
OL,20,Fdouble the radio audience. This was the
OL,21,Ffirst time the television audience
OL,22,Fexceeded the numbers listening on
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
