OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1981FThe first edition of Razzmatazz
OL,7,Fairs on ITV.
OL,8,
OL,9,FMusic-based children's programme. It
OL,10,Fwould run for nine series.
OL,11,
OL,12,FIt was produced by Tyne Tees Television
OL,13,Fand initially featured presenters
OL,14,FAlastair Pirrie and Lyn Spencer.
OL,15,
OL,16,FLater presenters included Brendan
OL,17,FHealy, Suzanne Dando and singer Lisa
OL,18,FStansfield, who joined the show when
OL,19,Fshe was 16.
